         <abstract>
            <p>We propose a discretization scheme for a numerical solution of elliptic PDE's, based on local representation of functions, by their Taylor poly-nomials (jets). This scheme utilizes jet calculus to provide a very high order of accuracy for a relatively small number of unknowns involved.</p>
          </abstract>
